room_title: Escape room "Off Limits" by Entrap Games in Omaha
room_description:
Your group of friends have been invited to an extravagant party and have been given the run of the mansion. All of it except for a single room, which you are not to enter under any circumstances. Of course, curiosity takes over, and you all stumble towards the secret room.
The door creaks open and the group steps inside. Moments later, the door shuts and locks! There doesn’t seem to be a way out – but surely there must be something! You have to find a way out of here, and fast - mysterious items reveal a dark side to this room’s owner.
